---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Join the Waitlist — TradeAnchor AI" description="Get early access to TradeAnchor AI and the Academy launch.">
  <section class="pt-14 pb-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Join the waitlist</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl">
      This is a mockup form (no backend). Wire it later to your email provider or database.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <form class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6" action="#" method="post">
        <label class="block text-sm text-neutral-300">Email</label>
        <input
          class="mt-2 w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-950/40 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder:text-neutral-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-400/40"
          type="email"
          name="email"
          placeholder="you@domain.com"
          required
        />

        <label class="mt-4 block text-sm text-neutral-300">What are you most interested in?</label>
        <select
          class="mt-2 w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-950/40 px-4 py-3 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-400/40"
          name="interest"
        >
          <option>Automated limit adjustments</option>
          <option>Ranked buy list</option>
          <option>Academy content</option>
          <option>Audit trail transparency</option>
        </select>

        <button
          class="mt-6 w-full rounded-2xl bg-sky-500 px-5 py-3 font-medium text-neutral-950 hover:bg-sky-400 transition"
          type="submit"
        >
          Request access
        </button>

        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-400">
          By submitting, you agree to receive product updates. Unsubscribe anytime.
        </p>
      </form>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">What you’ll get</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-neutral-300">
          <li>• Early product demos & build updates</li>
          <li>• Academy launch lessons</li>
          <li>• Pricing & feature announcements</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl bg-sky-500/10 p-4 ring-1 ring-sky-400/20">
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-200">
            Next: add a backend (Astro actions / API route) to store emails, then connect your email tool.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

